# ── AI/LLM witnesses — sourced from ~/Documents/Papers/AI_LLM/ ──
# paperCategory = "ai-llm" → rendered into src/witnesses_ai_llm.rs.
# Covers all 93 files in AI_LLM/: classical AI paper PDFs (12) +
# modern agent/LLM papers (80+) + classical-ai-foundations.md.
# Classical AI paper PDFs (Fikes/Nilsson, Aamodt/Plaza, etc.) also appear
# in witnesses-cognition.ttl as breed witnesses; here they appear under
# "ai-llm" to ensure the AI_LLM/ directory is fully represented.

# ── Classical AI papers (PDF copies in AI_LLM/) ──

